  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Statement from the Ambassadors of the G 19+ on Yemen
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
  
  <div class="column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    A statement from the G 19+ countries on the situation in Yemen.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
